Fonts
-----
- Gentium Basic is a bit too dense. Still not quite as readable as
  LinoType Birka.
- Find a good, condensed, free monospace font. 
	Candidates: 
		* Latin Modern Mono (http://www.fontsquirrel.com/fonts/Latin-Modern-Mono)
		* Inconsolata (http://www.levien.com/type/myfonts/inconsolata.html)
- Find a good, condensed, free sans font.
	Candidates:
		* Delicious (http://www.josbuivenga.demon.nl/delicious.html)
